room_title: Escape room "Antidote" by Locked: Escape Game in Nashville
room_description: Welcome to your first day as a research scientist at BTC Laboratories! You are one of the fortunate few selected to work at our state of the art facility. You discover you have all been exposed to a deadly gas and have but only an hour to devise an antidote. Are you smart enough to save you and your friends? Can you think quickly under pressure?
